column4: Finaly: A new OO.o build for Mac! Now I can stop using ssh -X to use OO on it :-P

Anyway. I'm interested in helping out the Ubuntu project. But I can't code, barley am able to draw a stick figure, and can't write that well. How can I help (besides hanging out here, learning and passing on what I learn)
are u a unicorn or not
I know I don't have to code. But I can't do artwork, or even write decent documentation.....
do u know any other langs than english
A very slight amount of Spanish and Esperanto, no where near fluint in either.
Heh. Yeh, but I'm not a very good technical writer.
Or fiction, but that's another story :-P
u dont need to be a "very good writer"
I just need to know how to spell "you".
kind of silly to give you this
